name: MetaCene
description: MetaCene is a meta-MMO platform for gamers to entertain, govern, and create. It will be the next-gen blockchain MMORPG homeland for mass players. MetaCene innovates with AI integration and player-driven mod editing, while offering a unique gaming experience with free ownership, REALMS-based serverfi, and PVP-driven wealth creation, promising excitement and diversity for players of all types. MetaCene pioneers technological innovation with the UE5 Engine, offers in-game SDK for token swaps and NFT trading, and grants players autonomy over their data, promising a captivating gaming experience with high-quality visuals, economic opportunities, and player empowerment.
